Title: Principles of Biostatistics
Author: কিম্বের্লী গৌভরিউ
Summary:
Principles of Biostatistics 2nd Edition, authored by Kimberley Gauvreau and Marcello Pagano, is a book that offers students an introduction to statistical procedures through which public health, medical and life sciences students can conduct and evaluate research. It comprises of examples with real data that bring the content to life.
